author: Cleo Abram
description:
This is an airless tire, which means it doesn’t pop when punctured!

That’s REALLY important because this tire is for a truck headed to…the moon.

 But if it’s so great, why don’t we use it on Earth??

If you want to see the crazy robot arm on this truck, subscribe!

#shorts #truck #moon #tech #airless #science
title: Why Don't We Use Airless Tires Yet?
